Namora AI is a GPT-4 powered chrome extension to write personalized messages from LinkedIn profiles!

Simply go to a LinkedIn profile that you want to reach out to and press the shortcut "ALT" + "O" and lets GPT-4 do its magic 🪄🪄

We will take personalize the message and make it contextual to your own data that you set in your account 🤝
